**/buzola.gen.ts
# wrangler.jsonc is generated (DO NOT hand-edit) but COMMITTED: its `migrations` array is the only
# durable record of a worker's Durable Object migration history. The deploy runner clones the repo and
# regenerates the config from the committed one — without it, a fresh clone fresh-gens migrations from
# scratch, shifting tags when a DO class is added/removed, and `wrangler deploy` fails (code 10074).
# Regenerate with `bun run oblaka` after a resource-graph change and commit the result.
**/worker-configuration.d.ts
